QuestData.Title: Steal Them Back
QuestData.Description: <This empty crate of supplies is clearly marked with Kul Tiran signage. These must be the spoils of their raids on the farms of the valley.$b$bThe citizens would probably like their supplies back if there are any left.>
QuestData.CompletionText: Keep an eye out for anything useful. This place is very dangerous.
QuestData.RewardText: It's not stealing if we're stealing them back. Hey! Are those my lucky anchors?
